long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This app converts photos into cartoons in one click.
It's free and easy, no registration or software download needed. Just click Open Photo to load your photo.
You can choose a image file to convert from your computer or from Google Drive.
Provides Photo to Cartoon Converter, Vintage Photo Effect, Photo to Pencil Sketch, Photo to Oil Painting.

These Photo Effects are an easy and fun way to enhance your personal photos. It makes your photos beautiful with easy and powerful editing tools. 
Multiple filters and effects including Cartoon, Vintage, Sketch, Oil Painting, Glass, and more.

Provides Resize Photo Tool, This tool will help you to resize any image fast and easy. Just select a photo, resize it and save it to your hard drive.
